 data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3616292\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ugr1665702834531.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ugr1665702834531.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ugr1665702834531.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ugr1665702834531\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Close (CanClose) [FRM]\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Window property of a form component that determines whether the user can close the form window by clicking the Close button in the title bar.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ugr1665702834531__section_w4284ab1b5b1_w4285ab1b5_w4286ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ugr1665702834531__table_d11633e1_d11634e1_d11635e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ugr1665702834531__table_d11633e1_d11634e1_d11635e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ugr1665702834531__table_d11633e1_d11634e1_d11635e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ugr1665702834531__table_d11633e1_d11634e1_d11635e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Default</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ugr1665702834531__table_d11633e1_d11634e1_d11635e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Undefined. The default will be used.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ugr1665702834531__table_d11633e1_d11634e1_d11635e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ugr1665702834531__table_d11633e1_d11634e1_d11635e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The user can close the form by clicking the Close button in the title bar.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ugr1665702834531__table_d11633e1_d11634e1_d11635e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ugr1665702834531__table_d11633e1_d11634e1_d11635e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The user can close the form by pressing <span class=\"ph keypress\">Ctrl+F4</span>. The Close button (if visible) is disabled.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ugr1665702834531__section_lhg_wtw_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d795416e142\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ugr1665702834531__table_d11636e1_d11637e1_d11638e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">Dependencies:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Caption</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">System Menu</span>\n                           must be <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ugr1665702834531__section_uwh_ytw_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d795416e200\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"ugr1665702834531__ul_f2w_ytw_swb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ugr1665702834531__li_d40451e1_d40452e1_d40453e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kno1665702715076.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Caption</a><p>Window property that determines whether the form window has a title bar. Valid values: True (default) or False.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ecw1665702715443.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>System Menu (SysMenu)</a><p>Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the Windows system menu and buttons to minimize, maximize, and close the window are available for this window. Valid values: True or False.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616292\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616292\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Close (CanClose) [FRM] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Close (CanClose) [FRM] Window property of a form component that determines whether the user can close the form window by clicking the Close button in the title bar. Value Description Default Undefined. The default will be used. True The user can close the form by clicking the Close button in the title bar. False The user can close the form by pressing Ctrl+F4 . The Close button (if visible) is disabled. Usage Dynamic? No Dependencies: Caption and System Menu must be True . Applies To Form Related Links Caption Window property that determines whether the form window has a title bar. Valid values: True (default) or False. System Menu (SysMenu) Window property of a form or application shell that determines whether the Windows system menu and buttons to minimize, maximize, and close the window are available for this window. Valid values: True or False. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}